Verse Glossary
Ready to start learning Verse? This glossary is here to help!

UEFNVerse Glossary
Verse is a new programming language, so if you‚Äôre an experienced programmer and you see something you don‚Äôt fully get, check this glossary.

If you‚Äôre new to programming, this glossary is also for you. We‚Äôve added definitions for a lot of basic programming terms, and you might just find the answers you need here!

